# Hotline Sanzu, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind
# Joy for some movement
JoyXY WASD deadzone 40 # Move with joy
CamXY mouse 50 # Move Cursor

# Triggers
BumperL Shift # Focus mode
BumperR Space # Bomb
TriggerL M2 # Melee
TriggerR M1 # Shoot

ActionA E # Inteact / Throw
ActionB Q # Cancel

# Menu Buttons
MenuL R # Restart
MenuR Escape # Options

Up !! ScrollUp # Scroll Menus
Down !! ScrollDown # Scroll Menus
